Package antlr4.parser

Class CBaseListener

java.lang.Object
antlr4.parser.CBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
CListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class CBaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements CListener
This class provides an empty implementation of CListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
